<h3><a href="index.php?itemid=147">Hunley Conservation Update</a></h3>
</div>
When the Hunley was raised from its original not so deep sea grave, I was amazed at how intact it was after spending almost a century and a half under water. Turns out it is much more fragile than previously thought. A new report by those in charge of the conservation effort details how fragile the sub is and how they plan save it.<br />
<br />
