<p>Posted by <a href="index.php?memberid=1">Tom</a> at 06:30 AM. Filed under: <a href="index.php?catid=3">Random Thoughts</a></p>
<p><a href="index.php?itemid=145#c" rel="bookmark">4 comments</a> &#8226; <a href="index.php?itemid=145">Permalink</a></p>
